headline.main: Indian Sikh Reports Being Shot in Arm; Police Seek Suspect
headline.print_headline: Indian Sikh Reports Being Shot in Arm; Police Seek Suspect

lead_paragraph: Police in a Seattle suburb say they are seeking a white gunman after an Indian Sikh man reported he was shot in the arm and told to "go back to your own country."
